Package: spatialbp
Type: Package
Title: 2D Continuous Spatial Piecewise Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Aidan Bindoff <Aidan.Bindoff@utas.edu.au>
Maintainer: Aidan Bindoff <Aidan.Bindoff@utas.edu.au>
Description: Extends 1D piecewise regression into two dimensions. Fits 2D spatial surfaces stitched together at 1D boundary curves to detect spatial regimes, affinity, and repulsion in continuous spatial fields.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Config/rextendr/version: 0.5.0
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc >= 1.65.0, xz
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
